title: Bucktown 3Bd 2Ba with In-Unit MESSAGE FOR VIDEO!
posting_body: This unit has three bedrooms and two bathrooms with hardwood flooring in the spacious living areas and carpet in the bedrooms.
The kitchen has beautiful wood cabinets and a dishwasher.
For convenience, this unit also offers central heat & air and laundry in the unit.
Located within steps of everything Wicker Park has to offer.
You can't beat this location, the blue line is just a 6 minute walk and can take you to O'Hare, Rosemont, Logan Square, River West, and the Loop.
7 Eleven, Jewel, Walgreens, and endless shops and restaurants are just down the street!
